			.pagination
				a(href="#").pagination-item <
				a(href="#").pagination-item 1
				a(href="#").pagination-item 2
				a(href="#").pagination-item 3
				a(href="#").pagination-item 4
				a(href="#").pagination-item >

		.category-content.category-content--align_r
			h2 Carpet
			p Elegant, comfortable and beautifully tactile, carpet remains a timeless option for any home whether your look is classic or more fashion forward. Renowned for superior noise reducing and insulating qualities, today’s carpet lets you create a space that's practical without compromising on style.

